# Hackathon project

- Follow **`AGENTS.md`** at the repository root for objectives, docs workflow, verification, and Cursor notes.
- Before major work, use **`docs/spec.md`**, **`docs/steps.md`**, **`docs/learned.md`**; keep **`docs/demo.md`** aligned with the real demo path.
- Prefer **small patches**, **few dependencies**, **demo-ready** UX (loading/empty/error, obvious happy path).
- Use project **Skills** when invoked: `/rapid-scaffold`, `/plan-feature`, `/integration-spike`, `/debug-with-evidence`, `/ship-demo`, `/judge-pass`, `/close-task`.
